@startuml
' Golden template: asynchronous fire-and-forget.
' Source scenario: a producer emits an event and does not block on a reply.
' Open arrow (->>) is the async message. The caller continues without waiting.
' Reserve the async arrow for genuinely non-blocking calls.
autonumber
participant "Checkout Service" as Producer
participant "Event Bus" as Bus
participant "Email Worker" as Consumer
Producer ->> Bus : publish OrderPlaced
note over Producer : returns immediately, does not wait
Bus ->> Consumer : deliver OrderPlaced
Consumer ->> Consumer : send confirmation email
@enduml
